286
00:24:56,337 --> 00:25:00,503
I wish to press it, but I'm not sure
what will happen if I do.

287
00:25:00,935 --> 00:25:05,535
- Let me see, now. Three, five,
twenty-two, seventy-four,

288
00:25:05,635 --> 00:25:07,535
- eleven...

