293
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:25,269
We are here, right here-
Bellasan Quadrant.

294
00:25:25,769 --> 00:25:31,204
About three million keks from Tau 14.
Why? Are you homesick?

295
00:25:32,038 --> 00:25:34,971
- Gotta have a home for that.
- Mmm.

296
00:25:35,071 --> 00:25:38,670
Translucent bipedal
mesomorphic embryonic male.

297
00:25:38,770 --> 00:25:42,704
Yes, yes, yes. This is all very
fascinating, but take a look at this.

298
00:25:42,804 --> 00:25:46,304
- It's a map. Can you read it?
- Can I read it?

299
00:25:46,404 --> 00:25:49,239
Of course I can read it.
Yes. Hmm.

300
00:25:49,338 --> 00:25:51,805
- So, what do you see?
- Ah!

301
00:25:51,905 --> 00:25:55,672
- Yes, this is PI'ochda.

302
00:25:55,772 --> 00:26:00,070
- And this- this-
this is... Solbrecht!

303
00:26:00,170 --> 00:26:03,070
And this- And this-
And this- What is this?

304
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:06,738
- That's, uh- That's lunch.
- What's lunch?

305
00:26:06,871 --> 00:26:09,571
- Mmm.

306
00:26:09,671 --> 00:26:14,739
Spaghetti derivative, meatballs- sort
of, anyway- and Caldoch droppings.

307
00:26:14,839 --> 00:26:19,071
- Who ate it before you did?
- Hey, hey!

308
00:26:19,171 --> 00:26:21,405
Ahh!

309
00:26:21,505 --> 00:26:25,005
- Tell you a secret. This guy's nuts.
- I'll tell you another.

310
00:26:25,105 --> 00:26:28,272
He's never wrong.
Where are we going, Gune?

311
00:26:28,372 --> 00:26:33,173
Ahh, the broken moon
of Sesharrim.

312
00:26:33,274 --> 00:26:35,205
Only 13,000 keks away.

313
00:26:35,305 --> 00:26:37,838
- Have Akima lay in a course.
- We're on our way.

314
00:26:50,307 --> 00:26:54,371
- What's on Sesharrim, anyway?
- The Gauol, an ancient race.

315
00:26:54,471 --> 00:26:57,105
- Great.
- This isn't a joyride, kid.

316
00:26:57,205 --> 00:27:01,373
When the Drej destroyed Earth,
they figured life adrift in space...

317
00:27:01,473 --> 00:27:05,039
would break us down,
wipe us out.

318
00:27:05,639 --> 00:27:09,774
Do you really want
those vile creatures to be right?

319
00:27:11,841 --> 00:27:16,273
- Just lay down and die?
- A little late.

320
00:27:16,406 --> 00:27:21,474
About 15 years too late to save the humans.
But it's not like we didn't have a good run.

321
00:27:21,574 --> 00:27:25,274
It's not about a good run.
It's about our survival.

322
00:27:25,374 --> 00:27:29,908
See, the Titan was truly visionary,
the most advanced ship in the universe.

323
00:27:30,008 --> 00:27:35,306
That ship has the power to reunite
the human race, to give us a home.

324
00:27:36,207 --> 00:27:39,074
And the only way to find it
is in your hand.

325
00:27:39,174 --> 00:27:42,674
So, you're really
counting on me, then?

326
00:27:42,774 --> 00:27:46,075
- We all are.
- Well,

327
00:27:46,175 --> 00:27:49,142
if I don't like
the way things are going,

328
00:27:49,276 --> 00:27:52,874
I'll show you how much
like my father I really am.

329
00:27:55,706 --> 00:27:57,540
I'll leave.

330
00:28:13,074 --> 00:28:15,708
Ahh, no place to
set down on the island.

331
00:28:15,808 --> 00:28:19,076
Land on that coral reef.

332
00:28:26,943 --> 00:28:30,242
We'll take the sled,
see if we can locate the Gauol.

333
00:28:30,342 --> 00:28:33,975
- Preed, you and Gune watch the ship.
- Watch the ship?

334
00:28:34,075 --> 00:28:37,409
- And keep the engines hot.
- Oh, yes. They'll be nice and toasty.

335
00:28:37,509 --> 00:28:41,510
- Hmm. - I'm not keen on the Drej
catching me with my trousers down.

336
00:28:43,143 --> 00:28:45,877
Welcome to Planet Sesharrim, Cale.

337
00:28:45,977 --> 00:28:48,874
- It stinks.
- Hydrogen trees.

338
00:28:48,975 --> 00:28:52,609
Clip one of those,
and we'll be blown to steaming bits.

339
00:28:53,743 --> 00:28:57,476
Hello? Anybody here?

340
00:28:57,576 --> 00:28:59,843
We're looking
for the Gauol.

341
00:28:59,943 --> 00:29:02,977
Now, what exactly
do the Gauol look like?

342
00:29:03,077 --> 00:29:05,975
