They don't get out much.

343
00:29:07,075 --> 00:29:10,676
We have a kid with a map here
that you guys should know about.

344
00:29:30,477 --> 00:29:33,911
I think we know
what happened to the Gauol.

345
00:29:35,078 --> 00:29:37,845
