434
00:40:17,295 --> 00:40:18,929
Akima!

435
00:40:22,829 --> 00:40:23,663
No!

436
00:40:50,262 --> 00:40:55,230
Akima's signal is getting stronger. I
think it's coming from the slave cages.

437
00:40:57,397 --> 00:40:59,831
- A Drej pod. What's in it?
- A human.

438
00:40:59,931 --> 00:41:02,398
- She's mine. I saw her first.

439
00:41:03,499 --> 00:41:04,962
