444
00:41:21,764 --> 00:41:26,063
I wonder if we might sneak a peek at the
new shipment before they go on the market?

445
00:41:26,563 --> 00:41:29,863
- You're not allowed.
- Traditionally, no. You're absolutely right.

446
00:41:29,964 --> 00:41:33,464
