I need a new slave rather badly.

447
00:41:33,598 --> 00:41:36,632
- Stop fidgeting, worm!

448
00:41:36,765 --> 00:41:40,199
And I can't wait till auction.
I have to be on the shuttle.

449
00:41:40,299 --> 00:41:44,231
I have an appointment to have my ear shaved.
It has to be booked months in advance.

450
00:41:44,364 --> 00:41:47,897
- You see my problem.
- Hmm.

451
00:41:47,898 --> 00:41:51,365
You're Iying. He's not a slave,
and you're not traders.

452
00:41:51,465 --> 00:41:53,399
- But- - He doesn't carry
himself like a slave.

453
00:41:53,499 --> 00:41:56,432
- Look at the way he stands.
Probably ex-military. - How...

454
00:41:56,533 --> 00:41:59,100
Akrennian traders always threaten before
they ask a favor. It's tradition.

455
00:41:59,999 --> 00:42:02,198
- And your robes are made
out of bedspreads.

456
00:42:02,298 --> 00:42:07,764
- Ah. - Just out of curiosity,
did we have a plan "B"?

457
00:42:16,399 --> 00:42:19,731
- Hmm. An intelligent guard.
Didn't see that one coming.

458
00:43:03,332 --> 00:43:05,433
Whoa.

459
00:43:54,270 --> 00:43:55,000
- This is it.

460
00:43:55,400 --> 00:43:58,301
- Are you in there?

461
00:44:00,468 --> 00:44:04,669
Well, if it isn't the captain.
What kept you?

462
00:45:27,705 --> 00:45:32,004
Do you see anything? It was really
small, like a cocoon or something.

463
00:45:32,137 --> 00:45:34,704
No, no, no.
Nothing like that. No. Mmm.

464
